{"tid":2142208,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"包裹藏丫叉案還柙逾70日後獲撒控手足 另涉「三罷」案罪成 判監4個月","createTime":"2020-08-06T08:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T10:40:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe872e8cffa8c771e6bb2ef1f8d028b85cd3837","tid":2142208,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:56:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7868&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOpHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=f050670e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7868</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#崔美霞裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤趙(22) #1111灣仔<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(2)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n(4)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n(5)無牌管有無線電通訊器具<br />\n<br />\n🛑控罪(2)、(4)、(5)罪名成立<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n判刑：<br />\n(2) 4個月即時監禁<br />\n(4) 3個月即時監禁<br />\n(5) $5000(從保釋金中扣除)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">📌刑期同期執行，4個月監禁(再減74日)<br />\n<br />\n考慮辯方提供的案例，裁判官酌情從刑期中扣減74天，辯方指受疫情影響，刑期上訴聆訊可能要在10個月後進行，希望等候上訴期間可予被告保釋外出。控方不反對擔保<br />\n<br />\n法庭雖然認為本案無上訴基礎，但考慮到被告的刑期，很有可能在刑期上訴前完成，所以裁判官准予被告人保釋<br />\n✅✅✅<br />\n保釋條件如下：<br />\n1. 保釋金$ 10,000，<br />\n2. 宵禁 22:00 - 07:00<br />\n3. 不得離境<br />\n4. 須交出所有旅遊證件<br />\n5. 居住在報稱住址<br />\n6. 更改住址須24小時前通知警方<br />\n7. 每周警署報到2次<br />\n<br />\n📌判刑理由後補&hellip;&hellip;</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9c8c329b11925ba0d78bc17a76d3eddbd17f9833","tid":2142208,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4472966634805e6b49e678485bf2065324ed1b9","tid":2142208,"uid":202425,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:04:58.000Z","msg":"坐完70